Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.69,0:01:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十九話 波蕾與亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊他們從亞古捷斯回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有兩架嗎?\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.27,0:01:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達呢?\n捷度怎麼沒回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的作戰計劃都被他耽誤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,著艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼放這麼多假隕石?\n擾亂視線,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢走,慎重一點,知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.25,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪一個笨蛋放這麼多隕石出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣很難分辨出\n哪個是敵人哪個是隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼笨怎麼可能是重建吉翁軍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.64,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船好像移動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人的船出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.39,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達一定在附近,無論如何要找出來\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,莫迪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想聽聽你們對露卡的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們對她有何看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與我們無關,她好像是喜歡捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.99,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?\n是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是這麼猜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若說捷度喜歡她\n我還可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.96,0:04:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個捷度是誰?\n莉娜的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.12,0:04:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什..什麼\n那捷度和露卡實際關係如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.54,0:04:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前情況不明朗\n捷度他很受女孩歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度阿\n露卡阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣阿!\n露卡她...她才不會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被完全包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再抵抗,我們便會行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已說我們會行動的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.89,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必嘴硬了,我特別小心\n才沒破壞你們的艙口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.84,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我想攻擊你們,大可用別的作法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.09,0:04:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有求於我軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來亞加瑪的待遇很差呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阿,飯難吃,艦長又囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冒生命危險戰鬥也沒有資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報出你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.72,0:05:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫捷度.桑達,你好,聽說妹妹受你照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.28,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,我拿ZZ高達當禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從各方面來看\n你都是危險份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問你自己的良心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良心?咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來找我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.72,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明\n他是很溫柔的大哥哥阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對每個女人都很溫柔嗎?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.98,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是!這是誤會!\n不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡真的是\nZ高達的駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是確認一下,別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少解開手拷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放捷度出來,他是我的朋友阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷的精神系統沒順利開動\n就是這個少年害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒調查清楚前\n不准你接近他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.18,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒氣質\n莫非當駕駛員久了也會這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.84,0:06:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此,露卡不應該在當駕駛員了\n不可以啊,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,你有說什麼嗎?\n我什麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才好像有人叫我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼哼..癡心到耳朵產生錯覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.92,0:06:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?我是...\n別在假隕石內亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個..我們是奉命來塗刷MS的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們刷那一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...\nZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求塗刷成新吉翁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是捷度嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻煩你們了\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是送給亞加瑪的好禮物阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔\n就這麼決定吧!開始工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.86,0:07:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道這樣\n我就恐嚇他們要擊沉這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.32,0:07:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼琴聲?我得叫莉娜學鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.03,0:07:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.78,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,好,我們盡情玩玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,有緣再會了\n希望那時是天下太平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉勸你最好別當駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虧我想安排你和妹妹見面\n我再也不理你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是大炮的發射路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.95,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,進入射程距離還要多久?\n20分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20分鐘嗎?\n露卡和艾莉能帶回捷度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2艘敵艦接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.09,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體人員準備戰鬥\n主炮準備發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了,Z高達,MK2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,捷度逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道,我們正在找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的聲音是從這房間傳出的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,放開我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!你是釣捷度過來的誘餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很難在接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.53,0:09:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就開始作戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.04,0:09:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK..好好聽著\n米加戰車的火箭炮只有4發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.13,0:09:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,米加火箭炮...\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.58,0:09:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我引開敵人的MS,你找捷度吧\n我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!是ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的人也會開ZZ高達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點對不起捷度\n這次我們一定要逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度竟然逃回到ZZ高達裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿,ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼..正面有垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.69,0:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋棄妹妹毒自一人逃走\n我看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿..追上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站著別逃阿,捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是捷度阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度本人在這裏阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼無法平衡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.65,0:10:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了...追過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.55,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我抓到你了,捷度.桑達\n捷度,你是何時跑到那裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你害的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少說廢話了!我要讓你和\nZZ高達死在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.88,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣被吸走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那是ZZ高達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.08,0:11:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?不是捷度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰在控制的!\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查坐在ZZ高達裏面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桑多拉在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在港口裏面\n能夠攻擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡的技術真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.36,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你們!\n我們可是替你把MS帶到這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,快進入ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.82,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓比查和莫迪上去你的MS吧\n咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,別妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.43,0:12:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度是要跟我玩的\n哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!\n你打算怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不把她交出去\n想要人就自己來搶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!還沒分出勝負阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.24,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動!米加戰車的來福槍\n把輸出功率調到最大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一炮就能使整個港口不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛,那我也辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必用來福槍的\n在飛龍的機動性面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk2根本構不成威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要怕,抓下駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.01,0:13:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼!把侵入者的MS收拾掉\n是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.15,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桑多拉照預定的出航\n我把波蕾和莉娜帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性能差這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.71,0:13:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是差在技術吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.93,0:13:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟重要的捷度離的越來越遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起..\n我們是不重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉想讓我等到什麼時候阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後方又來一架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的敵人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰怕你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了!太厲害了\n我太喜歡這種感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.69,0:14:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯進入主炮射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,準備發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你怎麼了\n你還沒離開亞古捷斯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,以莉娜當人質\n是不對的行為阿,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了來了,停下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\n你怎麼可以開MS在城市上空玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.91,0:15:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿..沙堆塌了\n是MS阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,不要玩了\n把莉娜還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥\n吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,又不陪我玩,只會喊著莉娜\n可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.56,0:15:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,這是不同的兩件事..\n我陪你玩,我陪你玩可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.35,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人!\n我不要你為了就莉娜而陪我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽話我就陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你救了莉娜就會走掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的阿\n是邱貝雷,上面那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,小孩子都到附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開莉娜,離開這裏\n我一定陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度你在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.04,0:15:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有說謊阿!在這裏\n開MS太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來\n不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,討厭阿,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜..\n哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.75,0:16:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿,波蕾!\n這裏是市區,你會傷到別人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.68,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭阿,捷度你只想著莉娜\n完全不關心我了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,我也喜歡波蕾阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.41,0:16:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又說謊了\n想用ZZ高達破壞邱貝雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你嫌我礙事阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.84,0:16:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,看清楚\n這是你長大的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想破壞亞古捷斯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.49,0:17:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只想著莉娜,還一直欺負我\n你好壞阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.43,0:17:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經傷到人了\n殺死人了阿,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哥哥你逼我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.07,0:17:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,你這樣任性殺人\n哥哥真的會恨你的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.61,0:17:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恨?哥哥會很我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不認為嗎?本來就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被恨...表示被討厭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她行動停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反應器掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.22,0:17:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為你知道\n你做不該做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是無法和哥哥打鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,精神系統無法啟動\所無法開動邱貝雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!波蕾不能開動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.40,0:18:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的波蕾\n居然使用精神系統超過負荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虧我在三交代她別靠近捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿,把莉娜還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然成功甩掉追兵\n但是還是找不到捷度他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.48,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們到處跑了好久..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.11,0:18:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不是把MS交出去\n我們現在八成玩定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對阿...捷度應該能自己逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!在亞加瑪發動攻擊前逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.41,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿\n捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪...在交戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!\n莉娜..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.67,0:18:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...時間超過了\n亞加瑪要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡在幹什麼?\n她在作戰阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是..是嗎..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還想跑去哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪,捷度逃脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是被甩掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.27,0:19:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆,順便一提比查和莫迪也要回來了\n可是...莉娜還是下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,亞古捷斯那邊發出訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們全部撤退\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.68,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮發射準備!\n目標是亞古捷斯引擎部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮瞄準亞古捷斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.23,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你在幹什麼?\n怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.56,0:19:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長,不可以開炮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯有很多市民跟小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道亞古捷斯有市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼做是為了救更多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.98,0:20:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也不能因此波及\n亞古捷斯的市民啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣算是正義之士嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.57,0:20:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法回答吧\n所以...所以我討厭大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是戰爭阿\n戰爭算什麼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.87,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮準備完畢,射程障礙物清除\n怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.31,0:20:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,發射, 開炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開炮了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.86,0:20:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,區住區應該沒有受到損害吧\n是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.01,0:20:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左轉,全速脫離\n是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.61,0:21:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桑多拉,桑多拉,請回答\n龍飛,邱貝雷,現在回去
